</dt><dd><p id="_61565a5f-21b3-bdc0-4a57-0bf9cae62576">Encryption of the message <stem type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>m</mi></math><!-- m --></stem> using a key of an asymmetric keypair <stem type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>K</mi></math><!-- K --></stem></p>
